      "role": "user",
      "content": "rebuild? how? i'm just staring at a screen that says i'm broke. everything i planned for—my house, my retirement, just my basic comfort—it's all gone in like a flash. i feel like a ghost. there's nothing left to fight for. i'm already at the bottom, i might as well just stay here.",
