    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i just dont see how those steps matter when the void is this big. it's not just about money anymore, it's like the whole version of my life and my identity just vanished. everything is quiet and empty. sometimes it feels like it would be so much easier to just stop struggling and accept that it's over. like, instead of fighting to breathe in an empty room, why not just let go?",
